Package me.lemire.integercompression

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ByteIntegerCODEC
    Interface describing a CODEC to compress integers to bytes.
    IntegerCODEC
    Interface describing a standard CODEC to compress integers.
    SkippableIntegerCODEC
    Interface describing a standard CODEC to compress integers.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BitPacking
    Bitpacking routines For details, please see Daniel Lemire and Leonid Boytsov, Decoding billions of integers per second through vectorization Software: Practice & Experience http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1002/spe.2203/abstract http://arxiv.org/abs/1209.2137
    FastPFOR128
    This class is similar to FastPFOR but uses a small block size.
    IntWrapper
    Essentially a mutable wrapper around an integer.
    Util
    Routine utility functions.
